name: CAD/AED
summary: The exchange rate between the Canadian Dollar (CAD) and the United Arab Emirates Dirham (AED). It indicates how many AED are needed to purchase one CAD. Fluctuations in this rate impact trade and financial transactions between Canada and the UAE.

name: CAD/AFN
summary: The exchange rate between the Canadian Dollar (CAD) and the Afghan Afghani (AFN). It indicates how many AFN are needed to purchase one CAD. This exchange rate is relevant for financial transactions between Canada and Afghanistan.

name: CAD/ALL
summary: The exchange rate between the Canadian Dollar (CAD) and the Albanian Lek (ALL). It indicates how many ALL are needed to purchase one CAD. It reflects the relative value of the currencies and influences trade and investment between Canada and Albania.

name: CAD/AMD
summary: The exchange rate between the Canadian Dollar (CAD) and the Armenian Dram (AMD). It indicates how many AMD are needed to purchase one CAD. This exchange rate is important for financial and commercial activities involving Canada and Armenia.

name: CAD/ANG
summary: The exchange rate between the Canadian Dollar (CAD) and the Netherlands Antillean Guilder (ANG). It indicates how many ANG are needed to purchase one CAD. This rate impacts financial transactions between Canada and Cura√ßao and Sint Maarten, where the ANG is used.
